nal Pass. For more information about refunds, licenses, subscriptions, and other matters pertaining to your purchase, view our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/legal/refunds-policy/\">refunds policy</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:53:\"Everything needed to get a personal project gamified!\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:76:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gamipress-personal-pass.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:53;s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"Passes\";s:4:\"slug\";s:6:\"passes\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:53;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:3;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:6:\"amount\";s:6:\"199.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:12677;s:4:\"slug\";s:22:\"gamipress-leaderboards\";s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Leaderboards\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-10-02 18:17:17\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-04-22 07:42:42\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:49:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=12677\";s:7:\"content\";s:2397:\"<strong>Leaderboards</strong> gives you the ability to easily create, configure and add leaderboards on your website.\r\n\r\nPlace any leaderboard anywhere, including in-line on any page or post, using a simple shortcode, or on any sidebar through a configurable widget.\r\n\r\nAlso, this add-on adds new features to extend and expand the functionality of GamiPress.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-leaderboardscreate-1\"></span>Ability to <b>create</b> as many leaderboards as you like.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-database-1\"></span>Ability to <b>configure the metrics</b> by which users should be ranked (the user rank, the points types and/or the number of earned achievements).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-sand-clock-1\"></span>Filter the leaderboard by a set of predefined <b>time periods</b> (today, yesterday, current week/month/year and past week/month/year).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-funnel-1\"></span>Configure a <b>custom time period</b> to filter the leaderboard on a range of dates you want.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-brush-1\"></span>Ability to configure the <b>display options</b> for each leaderboard.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-leaderboardsdragndrop-1\"></span><b>Drag and drop</b> options to reorder the leaderboard columns.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-search-1\"></span>Displayed leaderboards can be <b>filtered and sorted</b> without refresh the page.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to place any leaderboard anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcode embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to place any leaderboard on any sidebar.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-leaderboardsuserposition-1\"></span>Shortcode and widget to show <b>user\'s position</b> on a specific leaderboard.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-schedule-database-1\"></span>Ability to setup leaderboard <b>results cache</b> to improve loading time speed on large leaderboards.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-businessman-1\"></span>Ability to <b>hide website administrators</b> from the leaderboard.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"12693,12691,12695,12696,12694\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:59:\"Add leaderboards to intensify the gamification of your site\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:65:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/leaderboards.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:52;s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Professional Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"professional-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:52;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:14;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:13143;s:4:\"slug\";s:18:\"gamipress-progress\";s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Progress\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-10-05 16:44:22\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-12 10:50:08\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:49:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=13143\";s:7:\"content\";s:3015:\"<strong>Progress</strong> gives you the ability to easily show to your users their progress of completion of any achievement, step, points type, points award, points deduction, rank and/or rank requirement.\r\n\r\nWith just a few controls, you will be able to setup different progression looks at frontend to let your user know graphically their current progress of completion.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Progress add-on includes a <strong>block, shortcode and widget</strong> to render a gamification element progress anywhere included a progress based on a custom goal (points amount, achievements unlocked and current rank).\r\n\r\nAlso, this add-on adds new features to extend and expand the functionality of GamiPress.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-currentprogression-1\"></span>Ability to show the <b>current progression</b> of an achievement, step, points type, points award, rank and/or rank requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-eye-1\"></span>Easy controls with <b>live preview</b> to completely customize the progress look (text, progress bar, radial progress bar or images).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-gutenberg-1\"></span><b>Block</b> to display anywhere the progress of an element or based on a custom goal (points amount, achievements unlocked and current rank).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to display anywhere the progress of an element or based on a custom goal (points amount, achievements unlocked and current rank).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to display on any sidebar the progress of an element or based on a custom goal (points amount, achievements unlocked and current rank).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span>New <b>fields and attributes</b> on GamiPress blocks, shortcodes and widgets to manually show or hide the configured progress</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Show the progress as you want</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressplaintext-1\"></span><strong>Plain text</strong> Show the progress in text like \"3/4\" with the ability to customize the pattern to use.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressbar-1\"></span><strong>Progress Bar</strong> Responsive progress bars with options to decorate them with an stripe effect and also animate this effect.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressradialprogressbar-1\"></span><strong>Radial Progress Bar</strong> Dynamic radial progress bars with options to decorate them with the colors you want.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressimages-1\"></span><strong>Images</strong> Show the progress with images with the ability to customize their sizes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"15146,2101335,2101331,2101332,2101334,2101333\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:79:\"Attractively show to your users their progress of completion of any achievement\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:63:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/progress-1.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.3.3\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:15860;s:4:\"slug\";s:22:\"gamipress-progress-map\";s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Progress Map\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-10-19 20:11:51\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-04-16 14:05:46\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:49:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=15860\";s:7:\"content\";s:3182:\"<strong>Progress Map</strong> gives you the ability to easily create, configure and add progress maps on your website.\r\n\r\nPlace any progress map anywhere, including in-line on any page or post, using a simple shortcode, or on any sidebar through a configurable widget.\r\n\r\nAlso, this add-on adds new features to extend and expand the functionality of GamiPress.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmaps-1\"></span>Ability to create as many <b>progress maps</b> as you like.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapstype-1\"></span>Ability to configure different <b>progress maps types</b> (specific or all achievements of type and specific or all ranks of type).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmaphorizontal-1\"></span>Ability to configure the <b>direction</b> of the progress map (vertical or horizontal).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapleft-1\"></span>Ability to configure the <b>alignment of items</b> displayed (left, right or center for vertical and top, bottom or center for horizontal).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-brush-1\"></span>Ability to configure the achievements <b>display options</b> for each progress map.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-diploma-1\"></span>Ability to <b>hide the text</b> of coming achievements or ranks (text will by replaced by \"?\").</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapsdragndrop-1\"></span><b>Drag and drop scroll</b> for horizontal progress maps.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span>Integrated with the <b>official add-ons</b> that add new content to achievements and ranks.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to place any progress map anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcoe embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to place any progress map on any sidebar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Vertical and horizontal progress maps</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapvertical-1\"></span><strong>Vertical</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmaphorizontal-1\"></span><strong>Horizontal</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Vertically place the achievements where you want</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapleft-1\"></span><strong>Left</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapcentervertical-1\"></span><strong>Center</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapright-1\"></span><strong>Right</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Horizontally place the achievements where you want</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmaptop-1\"></span><strong>Top</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapcenterhorizontal-1\"></span><strong>Center</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressmapbottom-1\"></span><strong>Bottom</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"16580,16583,16575,16576,16578\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:65:\"Add interactive achievements and ranks progress maps to your site\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:66:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/progess-map-2.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:25139;s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"gamipress-notifications\";s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Notifications\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-10-24 19:06:39\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-18 08:22:25\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:49:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=25139\";s:7:\"content\";s:2494:\"<strong>Notifications</strong> gives you the ability to live notify to your users about new achievements, steps, points awards, points deductions, ranks and/or rank requirements completion.\r\n\r\nWhile your users are interacting with your site, they will get notified without refresh the page when an action gives them something related to GamiPress.\r\n\r\nAlso, you can configure text patterns to show as example the user name to make notifications more personalized.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-urgent-message-1\"></span>Ability to <b>live notify</b> to your users about new achievements, steps, points awards, ranks and/or rank requirements completion.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-moderate-comment-1\"></span>Ability to <b>selectively disable</b> which notify to your users.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-positioning-1\"></span>Ability to <b>positioning</b> the notification in 8 different positions.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-lifetime-1\"></span>Ability to set the <b>lifetime</b> of new notifications.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-clicktohide-1\"></span>Ability to enable the <b>click to hide</b> on notifications.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-volume-1\"></span>Customizable notification <b>sound effects</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-brush-1\"></span>Easy controls to customize the <b>background and text colors</b> of notifications.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-sand-clock-1\"></span>Ability to enable the notification <b>auto hide</b> and the delay to perform it.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-cancel-disable-1\"></span>Ability to <b>disable live notifications</b> checks making notifications work just on page load.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-text-tool-1\"></span>Ability to configure each notification <b>title pattern</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-achievementlook-1\"></span>Ability to configure the <b>achievements look</b> (thumbnail, earners, steps, etc).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-ranklook-1\"></span>Ability to configure the <b>ranks look</b> (thumbnail, earners, requirements, etc).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span>Integrated with the <b>official add-ons</b> that add new content to achievements and ranks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"25145,25148,25147,60568,25146\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:48:\"Instantly notify of any new reward to your users\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:66:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/notifications.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.3.0\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:2113669;s:4:\"slug\";s:16:\"gamipress-zapier\";s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Zapier\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2020-02-20 10:53:27\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-04-10 10:11:24\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2113669\";s:7:\"content\";s:2991:\"<strong>Zapier</strong> let\'s you integrate GamiPress interactions with thousands of third party web services, including Google Sheets, Slack, Mailchimp, Twitter, Zendesk, Dropbox, Instagram and more!\r\n\r\nIn just a few minutes, you will be able to <strong>send GamiPress information to any Zapier service</strong> with relevant information like user and achievement details when an user earns an achievement.\r\n\r\n<strong>Important:</strong> You need a <a href=\"https://zapier.com/pricing\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Zapier premium account</a> to get access to webhooks (only signing up on Zapier you will get 14-day trial of premium features).\r\n\r\n<span class=\"notice notice-info\"> <span class=\"dashicons dashicons-info\"></span><strong>Note:</strong> This add-on is designed to send data to Zapier (using GamiPress as trigger for a Zap).<br>If you need to receive data from Zapier (to use it as action for a Zap) you need our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-rest-api-extended/\">Rest API Extended</a> add-on.</span>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Sample Use Cases</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Email & SMS</strong> Send notifications when an user earns an achievement (e.g. Twilio, Gmail).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Social</strong> Share a custom content on any social network when an user earns points (e.g. Twitter, Facebook, Instagram).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Spreadsheets</strong> Add earning details to a shared spreadsheet or CSV file (e.g. Google Docs, Dropbox, Google Drive).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Mailing List</strong> Update your mailing list (e.g. MailChimp, Campaign Monitor, AWeber, SendGrid).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Contacts</strong> Add user details to your address book when earns a rank (Google Contacts).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>CRM</strong> Add leads/contacts and notes to your CRM (e.g Highrise, Salesforce).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Accounting</strong> Update user information in your accounting system (e.g. Xero).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Help Desk</strong> Add a ticket to your help desk system (e.g. Zendesk, Desk.com).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Team Chat</strong> Send an instant message to your team‚Äôs chat room (e.g. Hall, Slack, Hipchat).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-database-1\"></span>Data will be automatically <b>sent when user earns something</b> (an achievement, a rank, a points award, an achievement step, etc).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span>Connect GamiPress and you WordPress with <b>thousands of services</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-reload-1\"></span>Ability to <b>send a test</b> to preview data sent to Zapier.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"2113673,2113674,2113672\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:59:\"Connect GamiPress with thousands of services through Zapier\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:59:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/zapier.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:25;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Affiliate\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"affiliate\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:25;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:5;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:22;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Community\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"co