/span><b>Issue achievements automatically on Credly</b> when user earns an synced achievement.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-database-1\"></span><b>Import all badges</b> you already have on Credly to your site.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-businessman-1\"></span>Option to <b>auto-sync your users accounts</b> with Credly.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-gutenberg-1\"></span><b>Block</b> to place a Credly sync form to let users connects his account with Credly.</li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to place the Credly sync form anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcode embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to place the Credly sync form on any sidebar.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span><b>New fields and attributes</b> on GamiPress Achievements block, shortcode and widget to display only achievements synced.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"2123329,2123328,2123327,2123326\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:47:\"Sync achievements and user earnings with Credly\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:59:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/credly.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:22;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Community\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"community\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:22;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:29;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:24;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"eLearning\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"elearning\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:24;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"