an><b>Referral URL generator</b> where users can convert any website URL into a referral URL.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-performance-1\"></span>Block, Shortcode and widget to place user\'s <b>referrals counters</b> separated by referral types (visits or sign ups).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-gutenberg-1\"></span><b>Blocks</b> to place the affiliate ID and referral URLs anywhere.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcodes</b> to place the affiliate ID and referral URLs anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcode embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widgets</b> to place the affiliate ID and referral URLs on any sidebar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"860671,860670,860672,860673\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:78:\"Add a complete referral system to award users who refer visitors and sign ups.\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:62:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/referrals.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:25;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Affiliate\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"affiliate\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:25;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:5;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:22;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Community\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"community\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:22;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:29;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:51;s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Personal Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:13:\"personal-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:51;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:8;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:52;s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Professional Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"professional-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:52;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:14;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:13;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:39042;s:4:\"slug\";s:26:\"gamipress-restrict-content\";s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"Restrict Content\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-11-10 12:15:15\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-04-22 07:57:03\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:49:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=39042\";s:7:\"content\";s:5340:\"<strong>Restrict Content</strong> gives you the ability to configure several restrictions to any post or page until user completes all the requirements specified.\r\n\r\nLimit the content to be displayed, replace the links or images by the text you want or restrict completely the access and redirect the users that not meets the requirements.\r\n\r\nRestrict a <strong>portion of content</strong> anywhere, including in-line on any page or post, using a simple shortcode or on any sidebar through a configurable widget.\r\n\r\nIn addition, this add-on has the ability to restrict posts and portions of content by <strong>expending points</strong> and award those points to the post author, making Restrict Content your <strong>Sell Content</strong> add-on.\r\n\r\nAlso, this add-on adds new activity events and features to extend and expand the functionality of GamiPress.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"notice notice-warning\"> <span class=\"dashicons dashicons-info\"></span> <strong>Note:</strong> This add-on was designed to let you <strong>restrict content</strong> only. <br> If you want to restrict the unlock of gamification elements then you should check our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-restrict-unlock/\">Restrict Unlock</a> add-on. </span>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a post</strong> When an users unlock access to a post.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a specific post</strong> When an users unlock access to a specific post.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a post by meeting all requirements</strong> When an users unlock access to a post by meeting all requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a specific post by meeting all requirements</strong> When an users unlock access to a specific post by meeting all requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a post using points</strong> When an users unlock access to a post using points.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a specific post using points</strong> When an users unlock access to a specific post using points.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a portion of content</strong> When an users unlock access to a portion of content.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a specific portion of content</strong> When an users unlock access to a specific portion of content.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a portion of content on a specific post</strong> When an users unlock access to a portion of content on a specific post.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to a specific portion of content on a specific post</strong> When an users unlock access to a specific portion of content on a specific post.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-vault-1\"></span>Add content restrictions on any post by the next <b>requirements</b>:\r\n<small>Points earned.\r\nRank reached.\r\nAchievements earned.\r\nAchievements of a specific type earned.\r\nAll achievements of a specific type earned.</small></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-expendpoints-1\"></span>Let users to optionally unlock restricted content without meet the requirements by <b>expending points</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-expendingpointsrequirement-2\"></span>Add content restrictions on any post to be <b>unlocked just by expending points</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pay-1\"></span>Post <b>author</b> will earn the points expended (sell content).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-private-1\"></span><b>Restrict access</b> to users that not meets the requirements and redirect them to the page you want.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-contentrestriction-1\"></span><b>Restrict the content</b> output to users that not meets the requirements (text, links and images).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-restrictcontent-1\"></span>Ability to customize how <b>content restriction</b> should restrict the content:\r\n<small>Until read more tag.\r\nReplacing content with excerpt.\r\nTrimming the content to a desired number of characters.\r\nReplacing the full content.</small></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-restrictportion-1\"></span><b>Restrict a portion of content</b> anywhere through a block, shortcode and/or widget.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-cancel-disable-1\"></span><b>Render a list of all posts restricted</b> anywhere through a block, shortcode and/or widget.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-bulleted-list-1\"></span><b>Render a list of all posts that user got access</b> anywhere through a block, shortcode and/or widget.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Render post restrictions and/or access button</b> of a desired post anywhere through a block, shortcode and/or widget.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-eye-1\"></span>Blocks, shortcodes and widgets to <b>show and hide a portion of content if user meets a specific condition</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-accesuser-1\"></span>Grant access to a <b>specific users</b> or <b>by role</b> to a specific restricted post.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pin-1\"></span>Support to <b>all registered post types</b> with public access.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"41222,387857,387856,41223,387854,41221\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:64:\"Limit access to any post or page based on GamiPress interactions\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:69:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/restrict-content.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:37;s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"Memberships\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"memberships\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:37;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:17;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.8\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:14;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:1900200;s:4:\"slug\";s:25:\"gamipress-restrict-unlock\";s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"Restrict Unlock\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2018-03-12 13:50:56\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-02-07 14:38:25\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=1900200\";s:7:\"content\";s:3731:\"<strong>Restrict Unlock</strong> gives you the ability to configure several restrictions to any gamification element(<b style=\"color: red;\">*</b>) unlock until user completes all the requirements specified.\r\n\r\nAdd <strong>unlock restrictions</strong> to users by a set of requirements, by role or to specific users to any points awards, deducts, achievements, steps, ranks or rank requirements.\r\n\r\nIn addition, this add-on has the ability to restrict unlock by <strong>expending points</strong>, letting you setup a <em>\"pay-for-unlock\"</em> on any gamification element.\r\n\r\nAlso, this add-on adds new activity events and features to extend and expand the functionality of GamiPress.\r\n\r\n(<b style=\"color: red;\">*</b>) Gamification element refers to any of the configurable elements on GamiPress: <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/docs/getting-started/points-awards-and-deducts/\">points type awards and deducts</a>, <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/docs/getting-started/achievements/\">achievements</a>, <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/docs/getting-started/steps/\">steps</a>, <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/docs/getting-started/ranks/\">ranks</a> and <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/docs/getting-started/rank-requirements/\">rank requirements</a>.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"notice notice-warning\"> <span class=\"dashicons dashicons-info\"></span> <strong>Note:</strong> This add-on was designed to let you <strong>restrict the unlock of gamification elements</strong> only. <br> If you want to restrict content then you should check our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-restrict-content/\">Restrict Content</a> add-on. </span>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock an element</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock an element.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock a specific element</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock a specific element.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock an element by meeting all requirements</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock an element by meeting all requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock a specific element by meeting all requirements</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock a specific element by meeting all requirements.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock an element using points</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock an element using points.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Get access to unlock a specific element using points</strong> When an users unlock access to unlock a specific element using points.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-vault-1\"></span>Add unlock restrictions by the next requirements:\r\n<small>Points balance.\r\nRank reached.\r\nAchievements earned.\r\nAchievements of a specific type earned.\r\nAll achievements of a specific type earned.</small></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-expendpoints-1\"></span>Let users to optionally get access to unlock an element without meet the requirements by <b>expending points</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-expendingpointsrequirement-2\"></span>Add unlock restrictions on any element to be <b>accessed just by expending points</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-secured-account-1\"></span><b>Restrict unlock</b> to specific users or by role.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-accesuser-1\"></span><b>Grant access</b> to specific users or by role.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"1900361,1900362,1900363\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:50:\"Restrict users to unlock any gamification element.\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:68:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/restrict-unlock.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:37;s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"Memberships\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"memberships\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:37;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:17;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:15;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:2120223;s:4:\"slug\";s:21:\"gamipress-submissions\";s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"Submissions\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-11 11:25:29\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-15 11:44:29\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2120223\";s:7:\"content\";s:2048:\"<strong>Submissions</strong> lets you bring to your users the ability to unlock achievements and rank through a form submission that your website administrators can review to accept or reject it.\r\n\r\nIn just a few minutes, you will be able to place submissions forms around your site where your users will be able to <strong>request the unlock</strong> of any achievement and rank.\r\n\r\nIn addition, this add-on includes the ability to <strong>enable notes</strong> with the submission form where users can explain why they should earn it and an <strong>administrative screen</strong> to manage all submissions received.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-checkbox-square-1\"></span>Enable achievements or ranks of your choice for <b>admin reviewed submissions</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-edit-document-1\"></span>Optionally, you can enable a notes field to let users <b>provide an explanation</b> with the submission.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-text-tool-1\"></span>Settings to configure the <b>submission form texts</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-bulleted-list-1\"></span>Administrative screen to <b>approve or reject</b> any submission.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pay-1\"></span>Ability to <b>revoke</b> already approved submissions and restore the user awards.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Blocks and Shortcodes</b> to place any submission form anywhere.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widgets</b> to place any submission form on any sidebar.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-officialaddons-1\"></span><b>New fields and attributes</b> on GamiPress blocks, shortcodes and widgets to manually show or hide the configured submission settings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"