res.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon</strong> When an user redeems a coupon.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon with a minimum amount of points</strong> When an user redeems a coupon with a minimum amount of the desired points type.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon with an achievement</strong> When an user redeems a coupon with any achievement of the desired achievement type.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon with a specific achievement</strong> When an user redeems a coupon with a specific achievement.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon with a rank</strong> When an user redeems a coupon with the any rank of desired rank type.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Redeem a coupon with a specific rank</strong> When an user redeems a coupon with a specific rank.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-diploma-1\"></span>Ability to set <b>unlimited rewards</b> for a simple coupon.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-sand-clock-1\"></span>Make <b>time limited</b> coupons setting the start and end dates.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-progressplaintext-1\"></span>Ability to <b>limit the total number of uses</b> of a coupon.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-cancel-disable-1\"></span>Ability to limit the maximum number of uses of a coupon <b>per user</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-accesuser-1\"></span><b>Restrict</b> the coupon redemption to a specific users and/or roles.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-secured-account-1\"></span><b>Exclude users and/or roles</b> to be able to redeem the coupon.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-bulleted-list-1\"></span>All coupons redemption will be registered on <b>logs</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to place a coupon redemption form anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcode embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to place a coupon redemption form on any sidebar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"754549,754553,754555,754548,754547\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:74:\"Create coupons that users can redeem for points, achievements and/or ranks\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:60:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/coupons.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:25;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Affiliate\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"affiliate\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:25;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:5;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:37;s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"Memberships\";s:4:\"slug\";s:11:\"memberships\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:37;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:17;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:51;s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Personal Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:13:\"personal-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:51;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:8;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:52;s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Professional Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"professional-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";