y events and features.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>New exchange</strong> When an user makes a new exchange.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Exchange a minimum amount of points</strong> When an user exchanges a minimum amount of the desired points type.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-reload-1\"></span>Configurable <b>points exchange forms</b> to let users exchange points between the predefined points types.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pointsexchangesliveupdate-1\"></span>Points exchange forms details will be <b>live updated</b> (without refresh the page).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pointsexchangesrates-1\"></span>Set different <b>exchange rates</b> by each points type.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-cancel-disable-1\"></span>Ability to <b>disable exchanges</b> between specific types.</li>\r\n	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Shortcode</b> to place any points exchange form anywhere (with support to GamiPress live shortcode embedder).</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widget</b> to place any points exchange form on any sidebar.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pointsexchangestable-1\"></span>Shortcode and Widget to place a <b>points exchange rates table</b> anywhere.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"467902,467901,467903,467900\"]\r\n\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:61:\"Let your users exchange points between different points types\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:69:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/points-exchanges.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:35;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Enhancements\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"enhancements\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:35;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:39;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:52;s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"Professional Pass\";s:4:\"slug\";s:17:\"professional-pass\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:52;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:14;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":3:{s:10:\"singlesite\";s:5:\"49.00\";s:8:\"2-5sites\";s:5:\"89.00\";s:14:\"unlimitedsites\";s:6:\"129.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:1;s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:5:\"years\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:25;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:2118401;s:4:\"slug\";s:24:\"gamipress-points-payouts\";s:5:\"title\";s:14:\"Points Payouts\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2020-04-19 17:07:57\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-23 12:11:41\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2118401\";s:7:\"content\";s:1974:\"<strong>Points Payouts</strong> gives you the ability to bring to your users the possibility to withdrawal their points for money.\r\n\r\nIn just a few minutes, you will be able to <strong>place points withdrawal forms</strong> around your site where your users will be able to request a points withdrawal for money based on a predefined conversion rate.\r\n\r\nIn addition, this add-on includes options to set <strong>different conversions per points type</strong> or limit the minimum and maximum amount allowed per withdrawal.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-star-1\"></span>Enable any points type of your choice for <b>points withdrawals</b>.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-money-gamipress-points-1\"></span>Set different <b>conversion rates</b> per each points type.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-purchasepointscustom-1\"></span>Ability to place <b>points withdrawal form</b>s to let users withdrawal points for money.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-recommended-1\"></span>Support to <b>single or multiples points types</b> per withdrawal form.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-bulleted-list-1\"></span>Frontend <b>withdrawals history</b> with details of each withdrawal.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-checkbox-square-1\"></span>Settings to reject or mark as paid any withdrawal.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-pay-1\"></span>Ability to refund paid withdrawals and restore the points to the user.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-shortcode-1\"></span><b>Blocks and Shortcodes</b> to place any points withdrawal form anywhere.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-widgets-1\"></span><b>Widgets</b> to place any points withdrawal form on any sidebar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagination=\"yes\" auto_height=\"yes\" auto_play=\"yes\" delay=\"8\" alt_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"743609\" onclick=\"none\" images=\"2121587,2118408,2118413,2121588\"]\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:64:\"Let users withdrawal points for money based on a conversion rate\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:66:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/points-payout.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:25;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Affiliate\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"affiliate\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:25;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:5;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:21;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"eCommerce\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:10