3500;s:4:\"slug\";s:22:\"gamipress-admin-emails\";s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Admin Emails\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2020-02-17 13:29:47\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-02-17 13:29:47\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2113500\";s:7:\"content\";s:1760:\"<strong>Admin Emails</strong> let\'s you setup automatic emails when a user earns a certain element to inform to your website administrators on exact moment you want.\r\n\r\nIn just a few minutes, you will be able to build a personalized email to being sent on <strong>relevant events</strong> like when a user reaches a points balance, unlocks an achievement or reaches a rank among others.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Admin Emails includes a huge list of <strong>tags</strong> to let you display relevant information about the user who earned something to your administrator like the user current points balance, last achievements earned and current rank of any type.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Features</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-3\">\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-mail-1\"></span>Send <b>customizable emails</b> to your website administrator when a users earns a certain element.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-funnel-1\"></span>Set the <b>condition</b> you want: reach a points balance, unlock an achievement, unlock any achievement of type, unlock all achievements of type or reach a rank.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-star-1\"></span><b>Tags per type</b> to inform administrator about the user current points balance, last achievements earned and current rank of any type.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-businessman-1\"></span>Ability to <b>set the roles</b> you want to send emails.</li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"o-sync-email-1\"></span>Ability to <b>send a test email</b> to yourself.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Screenshots</h3>\r\n[kc_carousel_images img_size=\"full\" items_number=\"1\" tablet=\"1\" mobile=\"1\" speed=\"500\" pagina