s:3:\"low\";s:87:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-digimember-integration/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=2295042\";s:4:\"high\";s:88:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-digimember-integration/assets/banner-1544x500.png?rev=2295042\";}s:5:\"icons\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:85:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-digimember-integration/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=2295042\";s:2:\"2x\";s:85:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-digimember-integration/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=2295042\";}s:18:\"author_block_count\";i:0;s:19:\"author_block_rating\";i:0;}}i:61;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:1346;s:4:\"slug\";s:34:\"easy-digital-downloads-integration\";s:5:\"title\";s:34:\"Easy Digital Downloads integration\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-09-03 15:11:47\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-19 09:09:38\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:48:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=1346\";s:7:\"content\";s:4847:\"<a title=\"Easy Digital Downloads\" href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/?ref=4740\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> is a complete free eCommerce solution for selling digital and other non-physical products on your WordPress website. Easy Digital Downloads makes selling digital products easy in a light, easy-to-use plugin with all the features you need, and nothing you don‚Äôt.\r\n\r\nAdd <strong>gamification</strong> to your Easy Digital Downloads store to engage your users to increase your sales!\r\n\r\nThis plugin automatically connects GamiPress with Easy Digital Downloads adding new activity events and features.\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n 	<li><strong>New download</strong>¬†When a user publish a new download.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New purchase</strong>¬†When a user makes a new purchase (triggered 1 time on a purchase, independent of the number of downloads purchased).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New download purchase</strong>¬†When a user purchases a download (triggered on every download purchased on a purchase).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Specific download purchase</strong>¬†When a user purchases a specific download.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New free download purchase</strong>¬†When a user purchases a free download (triggered on every free download purchased on a purchase).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New paid download purchase</strong>¬†When a user purchases a paid download (triggered on every paid download purchased on a purchase).</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New sale</strong> When a user (vendor) makes a new sale.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Refund a purchase</strong> When a user refunds a purchase.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events By Extension</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/downloads/frontend-submissions/?ref=4740\">EDD FrontEnd Submissions</a></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-1\">\r\n 	<li><strong>New download approval</strong> When a vendor gets approved a new download</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/downloads/edd-wish-lists/?ref=4740\">EDD Wish Lists</a></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n 	<li><strong>New wish list</strong> When a user creates a new wish list</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Add to wish list</strong> When a user adds a download to a wish list</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Add specific download to wish list</strong> When a user adds a specific download to a wish list</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">EDD Downloads Lists</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n	<li><strong>Add to wishes list</strong> When a user adds a download to wishes list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add specific download to wishes list</strong> When a user adds a specific download to wishes list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add to favorites list</strong> When a user adds a download to favorites list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add specific download to favorites list</strong> When a user adds a specific download to favorites list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add to likes list</strong> When a user adds a download to likes list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add specific download to likes list</strong> When a user adds a specific download to likes list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add to recommendations list</strong> When a user adds a download to recommendations list</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Add specific download to recommendations list</strong> When a user adds a specific download to recommendations list</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/downloads/product-reviews/?ref=4740\">EDD Reviews</a></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Review a download</strong> When a user reviews a download</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Review a specific download</strong> When a user reviews a specific download</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Vendor gets a review on a download</strong> When a user (vendor) gets a review on a download.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Vendor gets a review on a specific download</strong> When a user (vendor) gets a review on a specific download.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">EDD Download Pages</h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>New download page</strong> When a user publish a new download page</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>New download pages approval</strong> When a vendor gets approved a new download page</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/downloads/edd-social-discounts/?ref=4740\">EDD Social Discounts</a></h4>\r\n<ul class=\"features-list cols-2\">\r\n 	<li><strong>Share download</strong> When a user shares a download</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Share a specific download</strong> When a user shares a download</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Features</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>From the download edit screen you will be able to setup an amount of points to award customers for purchase it.</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:7:\"excerpt\";