iPress\">GamiPress</a>!</p>\n<p>This plugin automatically connects GamiPress with Easy Digital Downloads adding new activity events and features.</p>\n<h4>New Events</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New download: When an user publish a new download.</li>\n<li>New purchase: When an user makes a new purchase (triggered 1 time on a purchase, independent of the number of downloads purchased).</li>\n<li>New download purchase: When an user purchases a download (triggered on every download purchased on a purchase).</li>\n<li>Specific download purchase: When an user purchases a specific download.</li>\n<li>Specific download variation purchase: When an user purchases a specific download variation.</li>\n<li>New download purchase of a specific category: When an user purchases a download of a specific category.</li>\n<li>New download purchase of a specific tag: When an user purchases a download of a specific tag.</li>\n<li>New free download purchase: When an user purchases a free download (triggered on every free download purchased on a purchase).</li>\n<li>New paid download purchase: When an user purchases a paid download (triggered on every paid download purchased on a purchase).</li>\n<li>New sale: When an user (vendor) makes a new sale.</li>\n<li>Refund a purchase: When an user refunds a purchase.</li>\n<li>Refund a download: When an user refunds a download (triggered on every download refunded on a purchase).</li>\n<li>Refund a specific download: When an user refunds a specific download.</li>\n<li>Refund a specific download variation: When an user refunds a specific download variation.</li>\n<li>Refund a download of a specific category: When an user refunds a download of a specific category.</li>\n<li>Refund a download of a specific tag: When an user refunds a download of a specific tag.</li>\n<li>Get a new refund: When an user (vendor) gets a download refunded.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Events by extension</h4>\n<p>EDD FrontEnd Submissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New download approval: When a vendor gets approved a new download.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EDD Wish Lists:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New wish list: When an user creates a new wish list.</li>\n<li>Add to wish list: When an user adds a download to a wish list.</li>\n<li>Add specific download to wish list: When an user adds a specific download to a wish list.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EDD Downloads Lists:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add to wishes list: When an user adds a download to wishes list.</li>\n<li>Add specific download to wishes list: When an user adds a specific download to wishes list.</li>\n<li>Add to favorites list: When an user adds a download to favorites list.</li>\n<li>Add specific download to favorites list: When an user adds a specific download to favorites list.</li>\n<li>Add to likes list: When an user adds a download to likes list.</li>\n<li>Add specific download to likes list: When an user adds a specific download to likes list.</li>\n<li>Add to recommendations list: When an user adds a download to recommendations list.</li>\n<li>Add specific download to recommendations list: When an user adds a specific download to recommendations list.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EDD Reviews:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Review a download: When an user reviews a download.</li>\n<li>Review a specific download: When an user reviews a specific download.</li>\n<li>Vendor gets a review on a download: When a user (vendor) gets a review on a download.</li>\n<li>Vendor gets a review on a specific download: When a user (vendor) gets a review on a specific download.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EDD Download Pages:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New download pages: When an user publish a new download page.</li>\n<li>New download pages approval: When a vendor gets approved a new download page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EDD Social Discounts:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Share download: When an user shares a download.</li>\n<li>Share a specific download: When an user shares a download.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>New Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>From the download edit screen you will be able to setup an amount of points to award customers for purchase it.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Expand your Easy Digital Downloads integration</h4>\n<p>There are more add-ons that improves your experience with GamiPress and Easy Digital Downloads:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-edd-partial-payments/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Easy Digital Downloads Partial Payments</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-edd-points-gateway/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Easy Digital Downloads Points Gateway</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/gamipress-edd-discounts/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Easy Digital Downloads Discounts</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:497:\"<h4>From WordPress backend</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins -&gt; Add new.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Upload Plugin&#8221; next to &#8220;Add plugins&#8221; title.</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file and activate it.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Direct upload</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file into your <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Unzip the uploaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins menu on your WordPress admin area.</li>\n<li>Activate this plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:593:\"<h4>1.2.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>New events: Vendor gets a review on any/specific download.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed a wrong duplicity check for products with multiples categories and tags.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed typo on meta key name on duplicity check function.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Improvements</strong></li>\n<li>Avoid to grant access to any event on duplicity checks.</li>\n<li>Moved old changelog to changelog.txt file.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:93:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-easy-digital-downloads-integration.1.2.3.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:0:{}s:4:\"ta