>\n<li>Finish any course: When an user finish a course.</li>\n<li>Finish a specific course: When an user finish a specific course.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Lessons</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete any lesson: When an user complete a lesson.</li>\n<li>Complete a specific lesson: When an user complete a specific lesson.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Quizzes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Finish any quiz: When an user finish a quiz.</li>\n<li>Finish a specific quiz: When an user finish a specific quiz.</li>\n<li>Finish a quiz of a specific course: When an user finish any quiz of a specific course.</li>\n<li>Pass any quiz: When an user passes a quiz.</li>\n<li>Pass a specific quiz: When an user passes a specific quiz.</li>\n<li>Pass a quiz of a specific course: When an user passes any quiz of a specific course.</li>\n<li>Fail any quiz: When an user fails a quiz.</li>\n<li>Fail a specific quiz: When an user fails a specific quiz.</li>\n<li>Fail a quiz of a specific course: When an user fails any quiz of a specific course.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:497:\"<h4>From WordPress backend</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins -&gt; Add new.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Upload Plugin&#8221; next to &#8220;Add plugins&#8221; title.</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file and activate it.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Direct upload</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file into your <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Unzip the uploaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins menu on your WordPress admin area.</li>\n<li>Activate this plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1255:\"<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added 6 events related to pass or fail a quiz.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Improvements</strong></li>\n<li>Added support to GamiPress 1.4.8 multisite features.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added &#8220;Finish a quiz of a specific course&#8221; activity event.</li>\n<li>Added compatibility with LearnPress 3.0.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed issue on activity triggers with default specific id.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Improvements</strong></li>\n<li>Updated text domain to add support to wordpress translate (tanslate.wordpress.org).</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed issue with text domain localization constant dir.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed issue with text domain localization.</li>\n<li>Fixed issues on activity triggers with specific ids.</li>\n<li>Fixed issue on activity triggers with default user id.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added extra data on event log.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.8.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:0:{}s:4:\"tags\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:9:\"elearning\";s:9:\"elearning\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:10:\"learnpress\";s:10:\"learnpress\";s:3:\"lms\";s:3:\"lms\";}s:8:\"versions\";O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-learnpress-integration.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.6\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gam