/ul>\n<h4>For Sections</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete any section: When an user completes a section.</li>\n<li>Complete a specific section: When an user completes a specific section.</li>\n<li>Complete a section of a specific course: When an user completes a section of a specific course.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Courses</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enroll any course: When an user enrolls a course.</li>\n<li>Enroll a specific course: When an user enrolls a specific course.</li>\n<li>Complete any course: When an user completes a course.</li>\n<li>Complete a specific course: When an user completes a specific course.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Memberships</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enroll any membership: When an user enrolls a membership.</li>\n<li>Enroll a specific membership: When an user enrolls a specific membership.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Access Plans</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Purchase any access plan: When an user purchases a access plan.</li>\n<li>Purchase a specific access plan: When an user purchases a specific access plan.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Certificates</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Earn any certificate: When an user earns a certificate.</li>\n<li>Earn a specific certificate: When an user earns a specific certificate.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>For Assignments</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Submit any assignment: When an user submits an assignment.</li>\n<li>Submit a specific assignment: When an user submits a specific assignment.</li>\n<li>Pass any assignment: When an user passes an assignment.</li>\n<li>Pass a specific assignment: When an user passes a specific assignment.</li>\n<li>Fail any assignment: When an user fails an assignment.</li>\n<li>Fail a specific assignment: When an user fails a specific assignment.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:497:\"<h4>From WordPress backend</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins -&gt; Add new.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Upload Plugin&#8221; next to &#8220;Add plugins&#8221; title.</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file and activate it.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Direct upload</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file into your <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Unzip the uploaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins menu on your WordPress admin area.</li>\n<li>Activate this plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1113:\"<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added 8 new events related to enroll a course, a membership, purchase an access plan and earn a certificate.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed wrong course object passed to some events taht requires the course ID instead.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added 6 events related to quizzes (complete, pass and fail).</li>\n<li>Added the event &#8220;Complete a lesson of a specific course&#8221;.</li>\n<li>Added the event &#8220;Complete a section of a specific course&#8221;.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added support to LifterLMS Assignments.</li>\n<li>Added 6 events related to submit, pass and fail an assignments.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></li>\n<li>Fixed wrong parameters on events listener.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Features</strong></li>\n<li>Added support to GamiPress 1.4.8 multisite features.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-lifterlms-integration.1.0.6.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:0:{}s:4:\"tags\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:9:\"elearning\";s:9:\"elearning\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:3:\"lms\";s:3:\"lms\";s:6:\"points\";s:6:\"points\";}s:8:\"versions\";O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-lifterlms-integration.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-lifterlms-integ