omplete any quiz with a minimum percent grade</strong>¬†When an user finish a quiz with a minimum percent grade</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete a specific quiz with a minimum percent grade</strong>¬†When an user finish a specific quiz with a minimum percent grade</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete any quiz with a maximum percent grade</strong>¬†When an user finish a quiz with a maximum percent grade</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete a specific quiz with a maximum percent grade</strong>¬†When an user finish a specific quiz with a maximum percent grade</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Pass any quiz</strong> When an user successfully pass a quiz</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Pass a specific quiz</strong> When an user successfully pass a specific quiz</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Fail any quiz</strong> When an user fails a quiz</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Fail a specific quiz</strong> When an user fails a specific quiz</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete any lesson</strong>¬†When an user finish a lesson</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete a specific lesson</strong>¬†When an user finish a specific lesson</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Enroll in a course</strong>¬†When an user enrolls in a course</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete any course</strong>¬†When an user finish a course</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complete a specific course</strong>¬†When an user finish a specific course</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:29:\"Connect GamiPress with Sensei\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:59:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/sensei.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:24;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"eLearning\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"elearning\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:24;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:17;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:36;s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"Free\";s:4:\"slug\";s:4:\"free\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:36;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"downloa