ms integration</a>.</li>\n<li>Support for WPAchievements LearnDash activity to be imported to <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gamipress-learndash-integration/\">GamiPress &#8211; LearnDash integration</a>.</li>\n<li>Support for WPAchievements WooCommerce activity to be imported to <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/gamipress-woocommerce-integration/\">GamiPress &#8211; WooCommerce integration</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:497:\"<h4>From WordPress backend</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins -&gt; Add new.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Upload Plugin&#8221; next to &#8220;Add plugins&#8221; title.</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file and activate it.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Direct upload</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file into your <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Unzip the uploaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins menu on your WordPress admin area.</li>\n<li>Activate this plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:980:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<h4>From WordPress backend</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins -&gt; Add new.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Upload Plugin&#8221; next to &#8220;Add plugins&#8221; title.</li>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file and activate it.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Direct upload</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the downloaded zip file into your <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> folder.</li>\n<li>Unzip the uploaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Plugins menu on your WordPress admin area.</li>\n<li>Activate this plugin.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n<h4>How to import your data?</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to WP Admin area -&gt; GamiPress -&gt; Tools -&gt; Import/Export tab.</li>\n<li>At box &#8220;WPAchievements Importer&#8221; you will find settings to set to which achievement types, points types and rank types migrate every group of data.</li>\n<li>Click the button &#8220;Start Importing Data&#8221; and wait until process gets finished.</li>\n<li>That&#8217;s all!</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:306:\"<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support to GamiPress 1.5.1 relationships since P2P has been deprecated.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support for GamiPress ranks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added cleanup process before start.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.1.0.3.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:0:{}s:4:\"tags\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:11:\"achievement\";s:11:\"achievement\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:12:\"gamification\";s:6:\"gamify\";s:6:\"gamify\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:9:\"gamipress\";s:5:\"point\";s:5:\"point\";}s:8:\"versions\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/gamipress-wpachievements-importer.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-wpachievements-importer/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=1754028\";s:2:\"2x\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/gamipress-wpachievements-importer/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=1754028\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}i:99;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:2116416;s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"automatorwp-integration\";s:5:\"title\";s:23:\"AutomatorWP integration\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2020-03-31 11:15:33\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-05-12 09:51:07\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2116416\";s:7:\"content\";s:814:\"<a href=\"https://automatorwp.com\">AutomatorWP</a> is a flexible and open-source plugin that let\'s you connect your WordPress plugins together and create automated workflows.\r\n\r\nYou can create \"automations\" linked to your WordPress activities and when any of them happen, you can make other things happen accordingly.\r\n\r\nYou can use these automations for automating sales, marketing, administrative tasks, learning and any other kind of processes you want letting you save time and get focused on your most important work.\r\n\r\nHere are some automations samples to give you a quick idea of the possible combinations:\r\n\r\nWhen user reaches a <strong>GamiPress rank</strong>.\r\nUpdate the <strong>user role</strong>.\r\n\r\nWhen user joins a <strong>BuddyPress group</strong>.\r\nAward a <strong>GamiPress achievement</strong>.\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:34:\"Connect GamiPress with AutomatorWP\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:70:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/automatorwp-brand.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:49;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"3rd Party\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"3rd-party\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:49;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:8;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:40;s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"Integrations\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"integrations\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:40;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:52;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}}s:4:\"tags\";b:0;}s:7:\"pricing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:6:\"amount\";s:4:\"0.00\";}s:9:\"licensing\";O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:7:\"enabled\";b:0;s:7:\"version\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"exp_unit\";s:4:\"days\";s:10:\"exp_length\";s:0:\"\";}s:7:\"actions\";a:0:{}s:7:\"wp_info\";b:0;}i:100;O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"info\";O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:2109328;s:4:\"slug\";s:27:\"activemember360-integration\";s:5:\"title\";s:27:\"ActiveMember360 integration\";s:11:\"create_date\";s:19:\"2017-09-06 19:15:29\";s:13:\"modified_date\";s:19:\"2020-02-11 10:32:03\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"link\";s:51:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=2109328\";s:7:\"content\";s:1404:\"<span class=\"notice notice-info\"><span class=\"dashicons dashicons-warning\"></span><strong>Important!</strong> This is a <strong>third party</strong> integration and hasn\'t been developed by the GamiPress team.<br>If you have any doubts, please, contact to the <a href=\"https://activemember360.com/support/\">ActiveMember360</a> team since they are the original authors of this integration.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://activemember360.com/\">ActiveMember360</a> is a WordPress membership plugin exclusively built for <a href=\"https://www.activecampaign.com/\">ActiveCampaign</a>.\r\n\r\nThe <a href=\"https://activemember360.com/docs/gamipress-extension/\">ActiveMember360 GamiPress Extension</a> provides an unsurpassed level of integration between ActiveCampaign and your WordPress site using GamiPress.\r\n\r\nThe ActiveMember360‚Äôs GamiPress Extension provides ActiveCampaign tag, list and contact field based conditions to award and deduct points and set requirements for achievements and ranks.\r\n\r\nIt also allows for the addition and removal of tags, and the setting of a contact field, when earning any achievement and rank, and the storing of point totals in a contact field.\r\n\r\nAll of the ActiveMember360 GamiPress Extension settings are fully integrated into the GamiPress settings. So if you are familiar with GamiPress there is no additional learning curve to using the ActiveMember360 GamiPress Extension.\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:38:\"Connect GamiPress with ActiveMember360\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:68:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/activemember360.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:49;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"3rd 