tiful theme to improve the design of its platform and with support with a great number of plugins.\r\n\r\n<h2>BuddyBoss Platform</h2>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.buddyboss.com/platform/ref/101/\">BuddyBoss Platform</a> is an open-source and 100% free full featured plugin for running online communities on WordPress.\r\n\r\nThe BuddyBoss Platform is based on BuddyPress which means that almost all BuddyPress plugins will work with BuddyBoss too including our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/buddypress-integration/\">BuddyPress integration</a> and our <a href=\"https://gamipress.com/add-ons/bbpress-integration/\">bbPress integration</a> (bbPress is for the forums feature).\r\n\r\n<h2>BuddyBoss Theme</h2>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.buddyboss.com/pricing/ref/101/\">BuddyBoss Theme</a> is a beautiful theme designed to power up the BuddyBoss Platform plugin look.\r\n\r\nThe BuddyBoss Theme includes support for a great number of plugins like LearnDash, Events Calendar, Gravity Forms, WooCommerce and of course GamiPress.\r\n\r\nOn the BuddyBoss website you can find demos of both solutions. In addition, you can see the BuddyBoss theme in action in <a href=\"https://demo.gamipress.com/\">our demo website</a>.\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:32:\"Connect GamiPress with BuddyBoss\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:62:\"https://gamipress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/buddyboss.svg\";s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:49;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"3rd Party\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"3rd-party\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:49;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:8;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":10:{s:7:\"term_id\";i:22;s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Community\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"community\";s:10:\"term_group\";i:0;s:16:\"term_taxonomy_id\";i:22;s:8:\"taxonomy\";s:17:\"download_category\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"parent\";i:0;s:5:\"count\";i:29;s:6:\"filter\";s:3:\"raw