sh\";s:4:\"link\";s:50:\"https://gamipress.com/?post_type=download&p=248631\";s:7:\"content\";s:3627:\"<a title=\"WPLMS\" href=\"https://wplms.io/\">WPLMS</a> is a full-featured WordPress LMS plugin that allows you to easily create and sell courses online. \r\n\r\nAdd <strong>gamification</strong> to your WPLMS courses to engage and motivate your students!\r\n\r\nThis plugin automatically connects GamiPress with WPLMS adding new activity events.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Events</h3>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">For Courses</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"features-list\">\r\n	<li><strong>Subscribe on a course</strong> When an user gets subscribed to a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Subscribe on a specific course</strong> When an user gets subscribed to a specific course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Start any course</strong> When an user starts a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Start a specific course</strong> When an user starts a specific course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Complete any course</strong> When an user completes a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Complete a specific course</strong> When an user completes a specific course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Complete any course with a minimum mark</strong> When an user completes a course with a minimum mark</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Complete a specific course with a minimum mark</strong> When an user completes a specific course with a minimum mark</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Review any course</strong> When an user reviews a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Review a specific course</strong> When an user reviews a specific course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unsubscribe on a course</strong> When an user gets unsubscribed from a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unsubscribe on a specific course</strong> When an user gets unsubscribed from a specific course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retake any course</strong> When an user retakes a course</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Retake a specific course</strong> When an user retakes a specific course</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-al